3799544cf5c9","tid":432962,"uid":51924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"香港人死邊個最開心? 自己諗"},{"pid":"698e7a055472fc64218ec24b51e6ed256f70f4e6","tid":432962,"uid":100368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57322125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57322125&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=968be767\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57322125&h=eae2b347\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57322125</a>油塘大本型外 青年墮樓昏迷送院<br />\n油塘商場「大本型」，上午11時21分，一名青年由高處墮下，重傷昏迷。救護員趕至將傷者送聯合醫院。</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57321494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57321494&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5a2d0b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57321494&h=44ab6e1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57321494</a><br />\n數少左?<br />\n哩到都有一個<br />\n沙田廣源邨 男子墮樓亡"},{"pid":"b6d69ab1f44d603b929efff28c3bafcd97992ed8","tid":432962,"uid":28358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"最近好似得SSR 甘比up ？"},{"pid":"3f6c5af33783893ebaafb0a8236b3b2357f9d392","tid":432962,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57321494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57321494&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5a2d0b62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171012%2F57321494&h=44ab6e1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171012/57321494</a><br />\n數少左?<br />\n哩到都有一個<br />\n沙田廣源邨 男子墮樓亡</blockquote><br />\n係喎<br />\n咁多年好似第一次自殺死7個 仲要只係一個上晝<br />\n<br />\n廣福邨11歲男生墮樓身亡<br />\n早上約7時55分，大埔廣福邨廣祐樓，一名穿著校服的男學生由高處墮下，倒卧地上，傷重昏迷，稍後由救護車送到那打素醫院搶救。警方封鎖現場調查，找到男童的家人及就讀學校的教職員，趕往醫院了解。墮樓男生11歲，相信他由10樓以上的走廊墮下。<br />\n男生的母親在醫院得悉噩耗後哭成淚人，而男生的胞兄亦身穿校服趕抵醫院，更雙膝跪地安慰母親，其他在場親友亦作出安慰。<br />\n大埔區議會副主席黃碧嬌亦去到醫院了解事件，她表示男童就讀小六，與父母及讀中六的胞兄同住事發大廈16樓，父從事飲食業，母為主婦。<br />\n現場消息指，與男童同住的祖母今年4月離世，而男童最近亦曾向胞兄透露，在游泳比賽中成績未如理想。<br />\n住在廣祐樓的街坊黃太，事發時剛晨運返家，途經大廈對開，聽得身後傳來「呯」一聲巨響，「返轉頭望一望，嘩！有個細路仔跌咗落嚟，趴喺地。」黃太直言好驚「個心都離埋」，對事件感到婉惜。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507777606_971c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507777606_971c.jpg&h=b55eaf0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油塘大本型外 青年墮樓亡<br />\n油塘商場「大本型」，上午11時21分，一名青年由高處墮下，重傷昏迷。救護員趕至將傷者送聯合醫院。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507781376_0ece.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507781376_0ece.jpg&h=2a60e9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大窩口邨男子燒炭亡<br />\n葵涌大窩口邨富碧樓，今晨9時半，一名30餘男子，被發現在單位內燒炭自殺，救護人員接報到場，經檢驗證實事主已告身亡。警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清河邨單位傳出異味 揭發男女倒斃屋內<br />\n早上10時29分，上水清河邨清照樓一個單位傳出異味，保安員拍門無人回應，於是報警。消防員到場破門入屋，發現一男一女倒斃屋內，警方正封鎖現場調查。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171012/large/1507780694_6a99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171012%2Flarge%2F1507780694_6a99.jpg&h=18e36178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田廣源邨 男子墮樓亡<br />\n早上7時許，沙田廣源邨廣松樓，一名約40歲男子從高處墮下，倒臥一樓簷篷，保安員發現報警。救護員到場經檢驗，證實男子已經死亡。警方正調查死者身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n疑受母親患病打擊 英籍男子上吊亡<br />\n早上約6時51分，上環文咸西街81號建南大廈，一名外籍男子，在家中露台用麻繩上吊，外傭發現報警。消防員到場將其解下，昏迷送瑪麗醫院，搶救證實不治。警方對事件展開調查，男事主Gordon英國籍，因為母親患病，他感到憂心不開心，懷疑因此輕生。"},{"pid":"bd19a660a919c6909e6ceab0cebb938786d2610f","tid":432962,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"聽返首歌先<br />\n個主音都係自殺死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KDOkMSf-F14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKDOkMSf-F14&d=6mBMeeO8Haym%2FeubmfjcPzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=13f7b140\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KDOkMSf-F14</a><br />\nThe Messenger"}]}